{"tid":2490262,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"戴咗口罩咁耐，差啲唔記得自己係樣衰添","createTime":"2021-04-15T12:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T13:54:35.000Z","uid":306565,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40b021f88338d75ff443f4c8850feeb791a4fcd4","tid":2490262,"uid":306565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"小弟天生樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日驚自己個樣嚇親人<br />\n就不時都想搵啲嘢遮住自己個樣<br />\n<br />\n自從戴咗口罩之後<br />\n我由樣衰變到普通人<br />\n唔洗面對自己樣衰嘅事實<br />\n都有返啲正常嘅social life<br />\n男仔冇再厭我毒撚樣<br />\n行街經過嘅女仔唔會主動避開<br />\n街市買餸啲姨姨都唔再叫我先生<br />\n<br />\n但係諗諗下<br />\n假如遲下唔洗戴口罩<br />\n我會由戴住口罩嘅普通樣變返樣衰<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8798f8da71d10297132eaefb19796a047c68eb5e","tid":2490262,"uid":306565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"哭撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557d5b140982ef5b7cc9dff77de0909570513bf7","tid":2490262,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"b43c6844f9f9b46e1feecf12a6c1024d7fb507c8","tid":2490262,"uid":2346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"整容啦<br />\n起碼其他人寧願面對你<br />\n男人無事業都可以靠個樣搵下食<br />\n阿姨我不想努力了"},{"pid":"a255838d17f177ad87c54095f0d35c0a6b6b4cac","tid":2490262,"uid":281150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:03:21.000Z","msg":"同意 戴咗口罩 搭巴士會坐我隔離嘅女性逐漸年輕化<br />\n差啲唔記得我係毒撚添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69788f44e24eb43304a124b3566164f687465217","tid":2490262,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"點都要面對現實架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c